      <title>海外资金涌入，年末中国股市上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-28/year-end-china-stocks-rally-takes-hold-as-foreign-funds-pile-in</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受2023年表现最差的一些行业的轮动和全球有利背景的推动，中国股市在年底前上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-28/year-end-china-stocks-rally-takes-hold-as-foreign-funds-pile-in</guid>
