    <item>
      <title>越南加大对开发商出售 12 亿美元债券的调查范围</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-28/vietnam-widens-probe-into-1-2-billion-bonds-sale-by-developer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[越南当局扩大了对陷入丑闻的开发商万盛发控股集团(Van Thinh Phat Holdings Group)因债券销售违规行为的调查，此案正成为该国打击腐败的焦点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-28/vietnam-widens-probe-into-1-2-billion-bonds-sale-by-developer</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 05:54:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台湾副总统满怀希望呼吁建立主权财富基金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-28/taiwan-vice-presidential-hopeful-calls-for-sovereign-wealth-fund</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾即将举行的选举中的一位副总统候选人在呼吁货币当局允许使用其数十亿美元的外汇储备中的一部分来设立主权财富基金后，正与强大的中央银行发生冲突。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-28/taiwan-vice-presidential-hopeful-calls-for-sovereign-wealth-fund</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 05:51:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>万科将以 6700 万美元出售悦榕集团股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-28/china-vanke-to-sell-shares-in-banyan-tree-units-for-67-million</link>
      <description><![CDATA[房地产巨头万科公司正在出售其在豪华连锁酒店悦榕控股有限公司中国子公司中的股份，这笔交易将为寻求应对中国房地产低迷的开发商带来4.8亿元人民币（6700万美元）的收益。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-28/china-vanke-to-sell-shares-in-banyan-tree-units-for-67-million</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 05:33:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于柴油和石脑油流量减少，俄罗斯石油出口下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-28/russian-petroleum-exports-decline-as-diesel-naphtha-flows-ease</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯石油产品出口周环比下降，其中柴油、石脑油和燃料油出货量大幅下滑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-28/russian-petroleum-exports-decline-as-diesel-naphtha-flows-ease</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国房地产市场悲观情绪导致铁矿石价格从 18 个月高位回落</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-28/iron-ore-drops-from-18-month-high-on-china-housing-pessimism</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资银行和券商预计中国住房建设的低迷将持续到明年，铁矿石价格从 2022 年 6 月以来的最高水平下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-28/iron-ore-drops-from-18-month-high-on-china-housing-pessimism</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 04:04:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国承诺提供市场援助，建筑商要求重新安排债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-28/korean-builder-taeyoung-asks-creditors-to-reschedule-its-debts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在泰永工程公司 (Taeyoung Engineering &amp;) 发布公告后，韩国试图安抚投资者。建筑公司要求重组其债务，再次引发了人们对去年引发该国信贷紧缩的金融工程类型的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-28/korean-builder-taeyoung-asks-creditors-to-reschedule-its-debts</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 02:37:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>降息希望导致国债上涨，金价连续第五天上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-28/gold-xauusd-holds-gains-as-treasuries-rally-on-us-rate-cut-optimism</link>
      <description><![CDATA[金价连续第五天上涨，这是自 11 月底以来最长的涨幅，此前对国债的强劲需求表明投资者对美联储明年放松货币政策充满信心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-28/gold-xauusd-holds-gains-as-treasuries-rally-on-us-rate-cut-optimism</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 00:26:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于原油库存进一步增加的迹象，油价保持下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-27/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-dec-28</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国库存增加以及技术指标疲弱的迹象，油价录得两周来最大跌幅后企稳。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-27/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-dec-28</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 23:56:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>债券、股票因美联储降息押注而上涨：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-27/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者为预期的美联储明年降息做好了准备，亚洲股市和债券跟随华尔街走高。金价逼近本月早些时候创下的历史新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-27/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 22:40:46 GMT</pubDate>
